<subSubSection id="B19122A3C508A208AD8271BBFC8F5CA5" pageId="161" pageNumber="162" type="remarks">
<paragraph id="06E06E3FDC59F690CF9D6C3D9B1367F0" pageId="161" pageNumber="162">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="5A2CE93285AE63AD287E8202BA823805" pageId="161" pageNumber="162">
This name has appeared several times in the literature (e.g., 
<bibRefCitation id="BC60D7A60FE16CAAC0D99F910ABCBA77" author="Bronn, HG" journalOrPublisher="A-M. Schweizerbart'sche Verlagshandlung und Druckerei, Stuttgart" pageId="303" pageNumber="304" refId="B53" refString="Bronn, HG, 1848. Index palaeontologicus, oder Uebersicht der bis jetzt bekannten fossilen Organismen. Erste Abtheilung. A. Nomenclator palaeontologicus, in alphabetischer Ordnung. Erste Haelfte. A-M. Schweizerbart'sche Verlagshandlung und Druckerei, Stuttgart" title="Index palaeontologicus, oder Uebersicht der bis jetzt bekannten fossilen Organismen. Erste Abtheilung. A. Nomenclator palaeontologicus, in alphabetischer Ordnung. Erste Haelfte" year="1848">Bronn 1848</bibRefCitation>
: 717; 
<bibRefCitation id="66F9AE40A9E3F7AF5119BB8821E7DBE4" author="Wenz, W" journalOrPublisher="Gastropoda extramarina tertiaria" pageId="333" pageNumber="334" pagination="2503 - 2886" refId="B542" refString="Wenz, W, 1929. Fossilium Catalogus I: Animalia. Gastropoda extramarina tertiaria vol. IX: 2503 - 2886" title="Fossilium Catalogus I: Animalia." volume="vol. IX" year="1929">Wenz 1929</bibRefCitation>
: 2773), but it is based on an error. 
<bibRefCitation id="627AB84FCB0A48831EB3C7A5F0439C84" author="Ferussac, AEJPJFd'Audebard de" journalOrPublisher="Memoires de la Societe d'Histoire Naturelle de Paris" pageId="308" pageNumber="309" pagination="132 - 164" publicationUrl="http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/item/23445page/148/mode/1up" refId="B144" refString="Ferussac, AEJPJFd'Audebard de, 1823. Monographie des especes vivantes et fossiles du genre melanopside, Melanopsis, et observations geologiques a leur sujet. Memoires de la Societe d'Histoire Naturelle de Paris 1 (1): 132 - 164, http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/item/23445page/148/mode/1up" title="Monographie des especes vivantes et fossiles du genre melanopside, Melanopsis, et observations geologiques a leur sujet." url="http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/item/23445page/148/mode/1up" volume="1" year="1823">
<normalizedToken id="4DDFA6A11DFF5C51AC5F646D2D132D57" originalValue="Férussac">Ferussac</normalizedToken>
(1823
</bibRefCitation>
: 154) actually described 
<taxonomicName id="C46F7F989EF65304252C35ECA7C2C19D" authorityName="Ferussac" authorityYear="1822" class="Gastropoda" family="Melanopsidae" genus="Melanopsis" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Melanopsis dufourii" order="Pteropoda" pageId="161" pageNumber="162" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="dufourii">
<emphasis id="9878B8F7C227A37FEA976181ED4BE072" italics="true" pageId="161" pageNumber="162">Melanopsis dufourii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
var. 
<normalizedToken id="8EC811ACC12A95C2D3BDA9248F99FB12" originalValue="ε">ε</normalizedToken>
and listed &quot; 
<taxonomicName id="97BD7E7A852A78915141BCF104A7CE45" genus="Fossilis" lsidName="Fossilis" pageId="161" pageNumber="162" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="3E1F699D3936C5BF4442A244FB28FA6F" italics="true" pageId="161" pageNumber="162">Fossilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, major. 
<normalizedToken id="67DE09888235B94E1597313C369C82C1" originalValue="Férussac”">Ferussac&quot;</normalizedToken>
in synonymy referring to plate 1 of the 
<normalizedToken id="9730B3F49DFC816EF47F6FE6EB27FD6F" originalValue="“Mélanopsides">&quot;Melanopsides</normalizedToken>
fossiles&quot; of his &quot;Histoire naturelle&quot; (
<bibRefCitation id="5F9A7D6086BEE75F15F3D83CB4E722A3" author="Ferussac, AEJPJFd'Audebard de" journalOrPublisher="J. - B. Bailliere, Paris" pageId="308" pageNumber="309" refId="B143" refString="Ferussac, AEJPJFd'Audebard de, 1819-1851. Histoire naturelle generale et particuliere des mollusques terrestres et fluviatiles tant des especes que l'on trouve aujourd'hui vivantes, que des depouilles fossiles de celles qui n'existent plus ; classes d'apres les caracteres essentiels que presentent ces animaux et leurs coquilles. J.-B. Bailliere, Paris" title="Histoire naturelle generale et particuliere des mollusques terrestres et fluviatiles tant des especes que l'on trouve aujourd'hui vivantes, que des depouilles fossiles de celles qui n'existent plus; classes d'apres les caracteres essentiels que presentent ces animaux et leurs coquilles" year="1819 - 1851">
<normalizedToken id="CD8E72CA55A4F1A62E9A5548BBC9EB28" originalValue="Férussac">Ferussac</normalizedToken>
1819-1851
</bibRefCitation>
; see also introduction for details about this work). However, in the captions of plate 1, it is given as &quot; 
<emphasis id="4AC4E025D3F6674A97AB70285DE0A8F6" italics="true" pageId="161" pageNumber="162">
<taxonomicName id="E4B2A1557EA7C2763018CF974B6F8DC4" authorityName="J. B. L. d'A. de Ferussac in J. B. L. d'A. de Ferussac &amp; A. E. J. P. J. F. d'A. de Ferussac" authorityYear="1807" class="Gastropoda" family="Melanopsidae" genus="Melanopsis" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Melanopsis" order="Pteropoda" pageId="161" pageNumber="162" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">Melanopsis</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicName id="414D7BD3AA0690FD00C2D06674D8912C" genus="Dufourii" lsidName="Dufourii" pageId="161" pageNumber="162" rank="genus">Dufourii</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
, var. 
<normalizedToken id="32DE6AD4265DC431C5EC91D5822F6177" originalValue="ε">ε</normalizedToken>
). 
<taxonomicName id="8B046734531CF1BEC50EAF6FC9A76D1A" genus="Fossilis" lsidName="Fossilis" pageId="161" pageNumber="162" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="4E21EF872DD6E90E06FC1D2917D2B933" italics="true" pageId="161" pageNumber="162">Fossilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<emphasis id="8A8F8BDC37C7CC2ED80B9C791333B168" italics="true" pageId="161" pageNumber="162">maxima</emphasis>
&quot;. Obviously neither 
<emphasis id="E1BA8550241F7E7DA112226D0A25ABA2" italics="true" pageId="161" pageNumber="162">major</emphasis>
nor 
<emphasis id="635C096AF146079C04552936AB4BF5CA" italics="true" pageId="161" pageNumber="162">maxima</emphasis>
was intended as species-group name by 
<normalizedToken id="198BD169EEB7D855BF4EE3A723124C9E" originalValue="Férussac">Ferussac</normalizedToken>
. Later, the name would have been a junior homonym of 
<taxonomicName id="178E42E44A610ECA37EBBB14FE6C4B0B" class="Gastropoda" family="Melanopsidae" genus="Melania" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Melania buccinoidea subsp. major" order="Pteropoda" pageId="161" pageNumber="162" phylum="Mollusca" rank="subSpecies" species="buccinoidea" subSpecies="major">
<emphasis id="EDDC88FD58F7783C4E5D887C30DEB1DA" italics="true" pageId="161" pageNumber="162">Melania buccinoidea major</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Grateloup, 1838.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
